1 occurred within the scope of Commission employment, duties, or responsibilities, or that such
2 person had a reasonable basis for believing occurred within the scope of Commission
3 employment, duties, or responsibilities, provided that the actual or alleged act, error, or omission
4 did not result from the intentional or willful or wanton misconduct of that person.
5 Nothing herein shall be construed as a limitation on the liability of any licensee for
